Class RemoteStoreHistogram

  • java.lang.Object

  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    BaseIncrementableTask, IncrementableTask, HistogramComputer

    public class RemoteStoreHistogram
extends MultiProviderHistogramComputer
    Class to get histograms from a remote service. If the image has a fixed size then a MultiDataStoreHistogram will build the histogram.
